race.description: Congrats Jayne Mckenzie Krc Maiden Plate
race.comment: Former Victorian galloper ATTACK FORCE (1) finished second at Sale two runs back but didn't measure up last time over 1980m at Tatura, finishing 22 lengths back in seventh. Will enjoy a drop in class so he is perfectly placed to score. THE IMMORTALS (6) improved last start to finish third over 1500m at this track after being in the firing line on the bend. Nicely placed to take this out. CLAW MACHINE (3) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 1400m at Sunshine Coast, beaten 8 lengths into eighth after being in the firing line on the turn. Finds an easier assignment and can turn things around. TOO DARN SMART (8) pushed forward from a wide draw last time and found a forward position then knocked up in the straight to finish eighth over 1200m at Sunshine Coast. Can feature in the finish.
